    "verification_notes": "Official site figures.house.gov returned 403 on all pages. DC phone (202) 225-4931 confirmed via BillTrack50 and multiple search results, matching prior unverified value. DC office is 225 Cannon HOB per clerk.house.gov 119th Congress listing and BillTrack50. Two district offices found: Mobile (107 St. Francis St., Unit 1930) with phone (251) 283-6280 per BillTrack50, and Montgomery (150 Dexter Avenue) with phone (334) 777-5700 per search results referencing figures.house.gov/contact/offices/montgomery. SenGov.com listed a different Mobile address (P.O. Box 40910, 907 Spring Hill Ave.) which may be outdated; BillTrack50 address used as more current. Social media verified via Ballotpedia: X (@repscfigures), Facebook, Instagram, YouTube. Bluesky account @repscfigures.bsky.social confirmed active. No Truth Social account found. No DC fax or district fax numbers found in available sources. Campaign site figuresforcongress.com confirmed active."
